item.title: 7. Contributing
item.description: Have a Question Found an Issue If you have an issue or you found a typo in the documentation, you can help us by opening an Issue. Steps to do before opening an Issue: Before you submit your issue search the archive, maybe your question was already answered couple hours ago (search in the closed Issues as well). Decide if the Issue belongs to this project or to Docker itself!
